It's  brown, has a pungent smell, but can you drink it? Though the Nelson Mandela Bay municipality insists the water flowing from the city’s taps is safe for consumption, a water expert has warned against it. What is the cause of the discoloured water? In this week’s ‘Behind The Herald Headlines with Daron Mann’, we delve into this issue. Subscribe for free: iono.fm | Spotify | Pocket Casts | Player.fm | Google Podcasts